com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.spec

Enum KontaktDeviceService

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<KontaktDeviceService>
      • com.kontakt.sdk.android.ble.spec.KontaktDeviceService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<KontaktDeviceService>

    public enum KontaktDeviceService
extends java.lang.Enum<KontaktDeviceService>
    Service Model describes service propagated by kontakt.io beacon after connecting to it. For more information refer to kontakt.io Beacon specification - version 2.0.
    See Also:
    kontakt.io Beacon Datasheet - version 2.0.
